query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS templatePreviewHistory (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  templateId INT NOT NULL,
  previewHtml TEXT NOT NULL,
  sampleData JSON,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (templateId) REFERENCES reportEmailTemplates(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  INDEX templateId_idx (templateId)
)
